title: Stormy Ocean with Dark Sky and Cliffs
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster,
medium: Pen and black ink on off-white wove paper
description: Delicately hatched sketch of dark, rough ocean crashing against rocks in bottom right. At left in distance, dark protruding land mass, with cloud covered sky. Miscellaneous pen strokes in all margins outside image.
name: Sketchbook folio
